    .col-md-10.col-md-offset-1
      %h1= t('top-nav.hardware')

      %hr

      %blockquote
        - rubytune = Sponsors.find(:rubytune)
        %p
          Our current bare metal server is sponsored by the team over at
          = succeed '.' do
            = link_to rubytune.name, rubytune.link, target: '_blank'

          .sponsor-logo.hardware-sponsor{ class: rubytune.class_name }
            %span.l-text-hidden rubytune.name

      %p
        All benchmarks are run on a bare metal server in order to achieve
        consistent and repeatable results. We
        %strong will not
        publish CPU results gathered on virtual hosts where we can not control
        our CPU allocation. The only results published are run on
        production level bare metal servers.

      %p
        The bare metal server is purchased from
